        <abstract> 
<p>CD’s seed paper in <hi rend="italic">Gardeners’ Chronicle</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 1: 255–8];</p> 
            <p>CD attacks Forbes’s "Atlantis".</p>
            <p>Considers solutions to floating problem. Decides to test Azores seeds.</p>
            <p>Photographs and drawings of CD.</p> 
<p>Plant movement experiments with <hi rend="italic">Hedysarum gyrans</hi>.</p> 
